GLIST - README
==============================================================================

Wow. someone's reading this.

WHAT IS GLIST?
	Glist is a mailing list manager, designed for stability, security
	and simplicity.

INSTALLATION

	See the file INSTALL

UPGRADING

	Upgrading is very simple. Should be done properly by just
	executing make install. But please see the Changelog file
	for configuration changes etc.

CONFIGURATION

	See the file CONFIG

DETAILS
	See the file DESIGN, and the documentation pages
	for each component.

AUTHORS
	Ask Solem Hoel <ask@unixmonks.net>, http://www.unixmonks.net

==============================================================================
